$B$H$3$m$G$7$g$&!#$3$l$O(B (i386 $B%f!<%6$J$i(B) <a href="#fdisk">fdisk(1)</a>
$B$ND>8e$K=P$F$-$^$9!#%$%s%9%H!<%kCf$K!"(Bdisklabel $B$r;H$C$F!"(B
