<a name="SoftUpdates"></a>
<h2>14.5 - Soft Update</h2>


<p>
Soft Updates $B$O!"(B
<a href="http://www.ece.cmu.edu/~ganger/papers/CSE-TR-254-95/">Greg Ganger
$B$H(B Yale Patt</a> $B$,Ds0F$7$?%"%$%G%#%"$K4p$E$$$F!"(B
<a href="http://www.mckusick.com/softdep/">Kirk McKusick</a>
$B$,(B FreeBSD $BMQ$K3+H/$7$?$b$N$G$9!#(BSoftUpdates $B$O!"%P%C%U%!%-%c%C%7%eA`:n$r(B
$BItJ,E*$K@@0M}$9$k$3$H$G!"%G%#%l%/%H%j$N%(%s%H%j$NF14|=q$-9~$_$H$$$&MW5a;v9`$,!"(B
FFS $B$N%3!<%I$+$i=|5n2DG=$K$J$j$^$9!#$3$l$K$h$C$F!"(B
$B%G%#%9%/$X$N=q$-9~$_@@-G=$KBgI}$J8~>e$,8+$i$l$^$9!#(B

<p>
Soft Updates $B$r;HMQ$7$F(B fsck(8) $B$r%P%C%/%0%i%&%s%I$G<B9T$9$k2DG=@@-$K$D$$$F$O!"(B
$B$^$@@(B OpenBSD $B$G$O<B8=$5$l$F$$$^$;$s$N$G!"(B
$B@@5$7$/(B shutdown $B$;$:$K=*N;$7$?$H$-$K$O!"$d$O$j(B
<a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=fsck&amp;sektion=8">fsck(8)</a>
$B$rI,MW$H$7$^$9$,!"$3$l$O>-Mh$N%P!<%8%g%s$G$OJQ99$5$l$k$+$bCN$l$^$;$s!#(B

<p>
Soft Update $B$r;HMQ$9$k$K$O!"(B

<p>
<b>option FFS_SOFTUPDATES</b>
<p>
$B$r$D$1$?%+!<%M%k$r%3%s%Q%$%k$7$J$1$l$P$J$j$^$;$s$,!"$3$l$O4{$K(B GENERIC $B$K$OF~$C$F$$$^$9!#(B

<p>
Soft Update $B$rM-8z$K$9$k$K$O%^%&%s%H;~$N%*%W%7%g%s$G9T$&I,MW$,$"$j$^$9!#(B
<a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=mount&amp;sektion=8">mount(8)</a>
$B%f!<%F%#%j%F%#$G%Q!<%F%#%7%g%s$r%^%&%s%H$9$k:]!"$3$N%Q!<%F%#%7%g%s$G$O(B
Soft Update $B$rM-8z$K$7$?$$$H$$$&$3$H$r;XDj$9$k$3$H$,$G$-$^$9!#(B
$B0J2<$O!"(BSoft Update $B$r;HMQ$7$F%^%&%s%H$7$h$&$H$7$F$$$k$R$H$D$N(B
$B%Q!<%F%#%7%g%s(B <i>sd0a</i> $B$r;}$D!"%5%s%W%k$N(B
<i><a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=fstab&amp;sektion=5">/etc/fstab(5)</a></i> 
$B%(%s%H%j$G$9!#(B

<pre>
/dev/sd0a / ffs rw,softdep 1 1
</pre>

<p>
sparc $B%f!<%6$X$NCm0U(B: sun4 $B$d(B sun4c $B$N%^%7%s$G$O(B Soft Update $B$rM-8z$K$7$F$O$$$1$^$;$s!#(B
$B$3$l$i$N%"!<%-%F%/%A%c$G$O!"$4$/8B$i$l$?NL$N%+!<%M%k%a%b%j$7$+%5%]!<%H$7$^$;$s$N$G!"(B
Soft Update $B$r;HMQ$9$k$3$H$,$G$-$J$$$N$G$9!#(B
$B$7$+$7!"(Bsun4m $B%^%7%s$J$iBg>fIW$G$9!#(B

<a name="Boot386"></a>
<h2>14.6 - OpenBSD/i386 $B$O$I$N$h$&$K%V!<%H$9$k$N(B ?</h2>
OpenBSD/i386 $B$N%V!<%H%W%m%;%9$OC1=c$J$b$N$G$O$J$/!"$=$l$,$I$N$h$&$KF0:n$9$k$N$+$r(B
$BM}2r$9$k$3$H$O!"$3$l$,F0:n$7$J$$>l9g$KLdBj$r2r7h$9$k$N$KLr$KN)$D$3$H$G$7$g$&!#(B
$B%V!<%H%W%m%;%9$K$O0J2<$N$h$&$J(B 4 $B$D$N80$H$J$kItJ,$,$"$j$^$9!#(B
<ol>
<li><b><i>$B%^%9%?%V!<%H%l%3!<%I(B (MBR: Master Boot Record):</i></b> MBR
$B$O%G%#%9%/$N:G=i$NJ*M}%;%/%?(B (512 $B%P%$%H(B) $B$N$3$H$G$9!#(B
$B$3$l$K$O!"%W%i%$%^%j%Q!<%F%#%7%g%s%F!<%V%k$*$h$S%Q!<%F%#%7%g%s%V!<%H%l%3!<%I(B
(PBR: Partition Boot Record) $B$r%m!<%I$9$k$?$a$N>.$5$J%W%m%0%i%`$,4^$^$l$^$9!#(B
$B$"$k<o$N4D6-$G$O!"(B"MBR" $B$H$$$&MQ8l$O!"(B($B%Q!<%F%#%7%g%s%F!<%V%k$r4^$`(B)
$B:G=i$N%V%m%C%/A4BN$N$3$H$G$O$J$/!"%G%#%9%/$N:G=i$N%V%m%C%/$N%3!<%I$NItJ,$@@$1$r(B
$B;X$7$F;HMQ$5$l$k$3$H$,$"$k$H$$$&$3$H$KCm0U$7$F$/$@@$5$$!#(B
