<a name="LargeDrive"></a>
<h2>14.7 - OpenBSD $B$G$NBgMFNL%I%i%$%V$K4X$9$kLdBj$O(B ?</h2>
<!-- XXXversion i386 changes for 3.5 -->

<p>
OpenBSD $B$O8=:_$d6a$$>-MhF~<j$G$-$k$I$N$h$&$J%O!<%I%G%#%9%/$h$j$b(B
$B$O$k$+$KBg$-$J%5%$%:$N%U%!%$%k%7%9%F%`$r%5%]!<%H$7$F$$$^$9$,!"(B
$B$$$/$D$+$N%$%s%?!<%U%'!<%9$G$O(B OpenBSD
$B$NM}O@@E*$J:GBgCM$h$j$b>.$5$J8B3&$,$"$j$^$9!#(B

