<h3>$B%F!<%W$K%P%C%/%"%C%W(B</h3>

<p>
$B%F!<%W$X$N%P%C%/%"%C%W$O!"%U%!%$%k%7%9%F%`$,$I$3$K%^%&%s%H$5$l$F$$$k$+$H$$$&CN<1$,I,?\$K$J$j$^$9!#(B
$B%U%!%$%k%7%9%F%`$,$I$&%^%&%s%H$5$l$F$$$k$N$+$K$D$$$F$O!"%7%'%k%W%m%s%W%H$+$i(B
<a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=mount&amp;sektion=8">mount(8)</a>
$B%3%^%s%I$r;HMQ$7$^$9!#$3$l$K$h$C$F!"$?$H$($P!"0J2<$N$h$&$J=PNO$,F@@$i$l$k$O$:$G$9!#(B

<pre>
# <b>mount</b>
/dev/sd0a on / type ffs (local)
/dev/sd0h on /usr type ffs (local)
</pre>

<p>
$B$3$NNc$G$O!"(Broot (/) $B%U%!%$%k%7%9%F%`$OJ*M}E*$K$O(B sd0a $B>e$K$"$j$^$9!#(B
$B$3$l$O(B SCSI $B8GDj%G%#%9%/(B 0 $B$N%Q!<%F%#%7%g%s(B a $B$G$9!#(B
/usr $B%U%!%$%k%7%9%F%`$O(B sd0h $B>e$G!"$3$l$O(B SCSI $B8GDj%G%#%9%/(B 0 $B$N%Q!<%F%#%7%g%s(B h $B$K$J$j$^$9!#(B

<p>
$B0J2<$O!"$5$i$K9bEY$J%^%&%s%H%F!<%V%k$NNc$G$9!#(B

<pre>
# <b>mount</b>
/dev/sd0a on / type ffs (local)
/dev/sd0d on /var type ffs (local)
/dev/sd0e on /home type ffs (local)
/dev/sd0h on /usr type ffs (local)
