<p>
$B:G8e$K!"B>$N%U%!%$%k%7%9%F%`$rA4It%G%#%9%/$K2sI|$7=*$($^$7$?$i!"(B
$B%^%k%A%f!<%6%b!<%I$K0\9T$7$^$9!#$9$Y$F$,0U?^$7$?DL$j$K?J$s$G$$$?$i!"(B
$B%7%9%F%`$O:G?7$N%P%C%/%"%C%W;~$HF1$8>uBV$KLa$C$F$$$F!"(B
$B$^$?;HMQ2DG=$K$J$C$F$$$k$O$:$G$9!#(B
</ul>

<a name="MountImage"></a>
<h2>14.10 - OpenBSD $B$G%G%#%9%/%$%a!<%8$r%^%&%s%H$9$k(B</h2>

<p>
$B%G%#%9%/%$%a!<%8(B (ISO $B%$%a!<%8!"(Bdd $B$G:n$C$?%G%#%9%/%$%a!<%8$J$I(B)
$B$r(B OpenBSD $B$G%^%&%s%H$9$k$K$O!"(B
<a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=vnd&amp;sektion=4">vnd(4)</a>
$B%G%P%$%9$r@@_Dj$9$kI,MW$,$"$j$^$9!#$?$H$($P!"(BISO $B%$%a!<%8$,(B
<i>/tmp/ISO.image</i> $B$K$"$k$H$7$?$i!"(B
$B%^%&%s%H$9$k$K$O0J2<$N$h$&$K$7$F$/$@@$5$$!#(B

<table border=0 width="650">
        <tr>
                <td nowrap bgcolor="#EEEEEE">
<pre>
# <b>vnconfig svnd0 /tmp/ISO.image</b>
# <b>mount -t cd9660 /dev/svnd0c /mnt</b>
</pre>
                </td>
        </tr>
</table>

<p>
$B%]%$%s%H$H$7$F$O!"$3$N%$%a!<%8$O(B CD $B%$%a!<%8$G$9$N$G!"%^%&%s%H$9$k>l9g$K$O$=$N<oN`$r(B
<i>cd9660</i> $B$G;XDj$9$k$H$$$&$3$H$G$9!#$3$l$O$I$N$h$&$J<oN`$N%$%a!<%8$G$b$=$&$J$N$G$9$,!"(B
$B$?$H$($P%G%#%9%/%$%a!<%8$r%^%&%s%H$9$k$N$G$7$?$i(B ffs $B$r;HMQ$7$J$1$l$P$J$j$^$;$s!#(B

<p>
$B%$%a!<%8$N%"%s%^%&%s%H$K$O0J2<$N%3%^%s%I$r;HMQ$7$^$9!#(B

