<a name="pciideErr"></a>
<h2>14.11 - $B=u$1$F(B!  PCIIDE $B$G%(%i!<$K$J$C$F$7$^$&(B !</h2>

<p>
PCI IDE DMA $B$OB?$/$N%O!<%I%&%'%"$NAH$_9g$o$;$K$*$$$F?.Mj@@-$,Dc$$$b$N$G$9!#(B
$B$G$9$N$G!":G6a$^$G$O!"(BIDE $B%I%i%$%V$H$N(B DMA $BE>Aw$N%5%]!<%H$rkp$C$F$$$k!"(B
$B$[$H$s$I$N!V<gN.!W$N%*%Z%l!<%F%#%s%0%7%9%F%`$G$b!"%G%U%)%k%H$G$O(B
$B$3$N5!G=$rM-8z$K$7$F$$$J$$>uBV$G=P2Y$5$l$F$$$^$7$?!#(B

<p>
OpenBSD $B$O@@Q6KE*$G!"@@_Dj$G$-$k:G>e0L$N(B DMA $B%b!<%I$r;H$*$&$H$7$^$9!#(B
$B$3$N$h$&$K$9$k$3$H$G!"$"$k@@_Dj$G$O%P%0$N$"$k%^%6!<%\!<%I$N%A%C%W%;%C%H$d(B
$B%P%0$N$"$k%I%i%$%V!"%1!<%V%k>e$N%N%$%:$J$I$NM}M3$K$h$C$F(B
$B%G!<%?E>Aw$N0-2=$r0z$-5/$3$9$+$bCN$l$^$;$s!#9,1?$K$b!"(BUltra-DMA $B%b!<%I$O(B
$B0-2=$r8!=P$9$k(B CRC $B$K$h$C$F%G!<%?E>Aw$rJ]8n$7$F$/$l$^$9!#(BUltra-DMA CRC
$B$,<:GT$7$?>l9g$K$O!"(BOpenBSD $B$O%(%i!<%a%C%;!<%8$r=PNO$7$F!"$b$&0lEYE>Aw$r;n$_$^$9!#(B

<pre>
wd2a:  aborted command, interface CRC error reading fsbn 64 of 64-79
(wd2 bn 127; cn 0 tn 2 sn 1), retrying
</pre>

<p>
$B2?EY$+<:GT$9$k$H!"(BOpenBSD $B$O$b$C$HCY$$(B ($B$=$7$F4j$o$/$P$b$C$H?.Mj$G$-$k(B)
Ultra-DMA $B%b!<%I$X$H2<$2$^$9!#(BUltra-DMA $B%b!<%I(B 0 $B$^$G9T$C$F$7$^$C$?$i!"(B
$B%I%i%$%V$O(B PIO $B%b!<%I$X$H2<$2$^$9!#(B

<p>
$B$b$7(B OpenBSD $B$,$&$^$/%b!<%I$r2<$2$i$l$J$+$C$?$j!"(B
$BESCf$G%^%7%s$,8G$^$C$?$j$9$k$h$&$G$7$?$i!"(B
<a href="../../ja/report.html">$B%P%0$NJs9p(B</a>$B$r9T$C$F$/$@@$5$$!#(B

<a name="RAID"></a>
<h2>14.13 - OpenBSD $B$N(B RAID $B%*%W%7%g%s(B</h2>
RAID (Redundant Array of Inexpensive Disks) $B$O!"0lBf$N%G%#%9%/$@@$1$N$H$-$h$j!"(B
$B$h$jNI$$@@-G=$d!"MFNL!"$=$7$F>iD9@@-$rF@@$k$?$a$K!"J#?tBf$N%G%#%9%/$r;H$&$?$a$N(B
$B;EAH$_$G$9!#(B
RAID $B$NFC<A$K$D$$$F$N>\:Y$J5DO@@$O!"$3$NJ8>O$NHO0O30$G$9$,!"$U$?$D$N=EMW$JE@@$@@$1$O(B
$B$3$3$GL@@3N$K$7$F$*$-$^$7$g$&!#(B

<ul>
<li>RAID $B$O%P%C%/%"%C%W$K$D$$$F$O2?$b$7$J$$!#(B
<li>RAID $B<+?H$O%@@%&%s%?%$%`$rC;=L$7$F$/$l$k$o$1$G$O$J$$!#(B
</ul>

$B$b$7!"$3$l$,$"$J$?$K$H$C$F?7$7$$>pJs$@@$C$?$j$7$?$i!"$3$l$O$"$J$?$K$H$C$F!"(B
RAID $B$NKA81$N$?$a$NNI$$=PH/E@@$G$O$"$j$^$;$s!#(B

<h3>$B%=%U%H%&%'%"%*%W%7%g%s(B</h3>
OpenBSD $B$O!"%=%U%H%&%'%"(B RAID $B$G$"$k(B RAIDframe $B$r4^$s$G$$$^$9!#(B
$B$3$l$K$D$$$F$N%I%-%e%a%s%H$O0J2<$N>l=j$K$"$j$^$9!#(B

