<h3>$B%O!<%I%&%'%"%*%W%7%g%s(B</h3>
<p>
$BB?$/$N(B OpenBSD $B$N(B <a href="../../ja/plat.html">$B%W%i%C%H%U%)!<%`(B</a> $B$O!"(B
$B$$$m$s$J<oN`$N%O!<%I%&%'%"(B RAID $B@@=IJ$r%5%]!<%H$7$F$$$^$9!#(B
$B$3$l$O%W%i%C%H%U%)!<%`$K$h$C$FJQ$o$j$^$9$N$G!"%O!<%I%&%'%"%5%]!<%H(B
$B%Z!<%8(B (<a href="../../ja/plat.html">$B$3$3(B</a> $B$K%j%9%H$,$"$j$^$9(B) $B$r8+$F$/$@@$5$$!#(B

<p>
$B$b$&$R$H$D!"J#?t$N%I%i%$%V$r0lBf$N(B IDE $B$d(B SCSI $B$N%I%i%$%V$H$7$F8+$;$F!"(B
$B$3$l$rI8=`$N(B IDE $B$d(B SCSI $B%"%@@%W%?$K@@\B3$7$F;H$&%?%$%W$NB?$/$N@@=IJ$,!"(B
