<h2>14.12 - IDE $B%G%#%9%/$KBP$7$F$N(B DMA $B%"%/%;%9$N6/@@)(B</h2>

<p>
PCI IDE $B$N%3!<%I$O!"%A%C%W%;%C%H$,2?$G$"$k$N$+$o$+$i$J$$$3$H$,$"$j$^$9!#(B
$B$=$N$h$&$J>l9g$K$O!"<!$N$h$&$J%a%C%;!<%8$,=PNO$5$l$^$9!#(B

<blockquote>
<pre>
pciide0: DMA, (unused)
</pre>
</blockquote>

$B$3$N%a%C%;!<%8$,=PNO$5$l$?>l9g$K$O!"%+!<%M%k%3%s%U%#%0%l!<%7%g%s%U%!%$%k$N(B pciide $B$N(B
$B%(%s%H%j$K(B 'flags 0x0001' $B$r;HMQ$9$k$3$H$G!"6/@@)E*$K(B DMA $B%b!<%I$G;HMQ$9$k$3$H$,$G$-$^$9!#(B
$B$3$l$O<!$N$h$&$J9T$K$J$j$^$9!#(B

<blockquote>
<pre>
pciide* at pci ? dev ? function ? flags 0x0001
</pre>
</blockquote>

$B$3$N@@_Dj$r9T$o$l$k$H!"(Bpciide $B%3!<%I$O!"%A%C%W%;%C%H$,<B:]$K$O$I$N$h$&$K$7$F(B
DMA $BE>Aw$r9T$&$N$+$rCN$C$F$$$k$+$I$&$+$K4X$o$i$:!"(BDMA $B%b!<%I$r;H$*$&$H$7$^$9!#(B
$B$b$7!"$3$l$,F0$$$F%7%9%F%`$,(B fsck $B$r9T$C$F5/F0$9$l$P!"$@@$$$?$$$&$^$/F0$$$F$$$k(B
$B$H8+$F$bNI$$$G$7$g$&!#$b$7!"$3$l$,F0$+$J$1$l$P!"$D$^$j!"5/F08e$K%O%s%0%"%C%W(B
$B$7$?$j%Q%K%C%/$9$k$h$&$J$i!"(B($B$=$N%A%C%W%;%C%H$N%5%]!<%H$,$^$@@DI2C$5$l$F$$$J$$(B
$B$?$a(B)$B!"(BDMA $B%b!<%I$r;HMQ$9$k$3$H$,$G$-$J$$$H$$$&$3$H$G$9!#$b$7!"$=$N(B PCI-IDE
$B%A%C%W%;%C%H$N%I%-%e%a%s%H$r8+$D$1$?$i!"$=$N(B PCI-IDE $B%3%s%H%m!<%i%A%C%W%;%C%H$r(B
$B40A4$K%5%]!<%H$G$-$k$h$&$K$9$k$?$a$NNI$$5!2q$@@$H9M$($F$/$@@$5$$!#$=$l$O@@=B$6H<T$N(B
Web $B%5%$%H>e$K$"$k$+$bCN$l$^$;$s$7!"EEOC$GJ9$$$F$_$F$bNI$$$G$7$g$&!#$^$?!"$b$7!"(B
$B$=$N(B PCI-IDE $B%3%s%H%m!<%i$,%^%6!<%\!<%I$N0lIt$J$i!"$I$N@@=B$6H<T$N$b$N$+$rD4$Y!"(B
$B$=$N@@=B$6H<T$N%j%=!<%9$rDI$$$+$1$^$7$g$&!#(B

<p>
$B<!$N$h$&$J%a%C%;!<%8$,I=<($5$l$k$3$H$G!"(BDMA $B%5%]!<%H$,M-8z2=$5$l$?$3$H$,(B
$B$o$+$k$H$$$&$3$H$KCm0U$7$F$/$@@$5$$!#(B

<blockquote>
<pre>
cd0(pciide0:1:0): using PIO mode 3, DMA mode 1
</pre>
</blockquote>

$B$3$l$O!"(B(ATAPI CD-ROM $B$H$7$F8+$($F$$$k(B) pciide0 $B$N(B channel 1$B!"(Bdrive 0 $B$,(B
